<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@100..900&family=Noto+Sans:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-5W0EZpGmCU5+M8G6k6kRvqY0C30tSXf98gkBCx9hqHV+Ic5Dbon2kzvPT2JZ9twd" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/styles.css">
  <%- include('../partials/ui-overrides') %>
</head>
<body class="bg-soft">
  <div class="app-shell min-vh-100 d-flex flex-column">
    <%- include('../partials/header', { user: user }) %>

    <main id="main-content" class="page-content flex-grow-1">
      <section class="surface-stack about-page">
        <div class="about-intro">
          <div class="about-copy">
            <div>
              <h1 class="page-title mb-2">About</h1>
              <p class="section-copy">This full-stack note-taking application was built with Node.js, Express, EJS, and MongoDB to demonstrate seamless front-end and back-end communication in a complete CRUD workflow.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-grid">
          <section class="about-section">
            <h2 class="about-section-title">Project Overview</h2>
            <p class="section-copy">This application connects a server-rendered interface with a MongoDB-backed data model to deliver a complete note management experience. It focuses on readable structure, rich editing, and reliable CRUD interactions.</p>
          </section>

          <section class="about-section">
            <h2 class="about-section-title">Key Features</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
              <li>Create, edit, and delete notes</li>
              <li>Rich text editing experience</li>
              <li>Search functionality for notes</li>
              <li>User authentication for personalized note storage</li>
              <li>Secure server-side validation and error handling</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="about-section">
            <h2 class="about-section-title">Technical Stack</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
              <li>Frontend: EJS, HTML, CSS, JavaScript</li>
              <li>Backend: Node.js, Express.js</li>
              <li>Database: MongoDB with Mongoose</li>
              <li>Authentication: Passport with Google OAuth</li>
              <li>Middleware: Express sessions and method-override</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="about-section">
            <h2 class="about-section-title">Architecture Overview</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
              <li>Organized MVC structure with routes, controllers, and models</li>
              <li>RESTful note operations using GET, POST, PUT, and DELETE</li>
              <li>Clear separation between server logic and UI rendering</li>
              <li>Secure data handling and validation throughout the app</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="about-section">
            <h2 class="about-section-title">Development Process</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
              <li>Initialized the Node.js project and organized folders for routes, controllers, and models</li>
              <li>Built the Express server to handle routing and incoming requests</li>
              <li>Connected MongoDB and defined the application data models</li>
              <li>Implemented full CRUD functionality for notes</li>
              <li>Created a responsive front-end using EJS templates</li>
              <li>Integrated authentication for user-specific note access</li>
              <li>Added validation and error handling for a more robust experience</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="about-section">
            <h2 class="about-section-title">Purpose</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
              <li>Server-side JavaScript development</li>
              <li>REST API design and implementation</li>
              <li>Front-end and back-end integration</li>
              <li>Database design and data management</li>
              <li>Authentication and session handling</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        </div>

        <section class="about-footer-note">
          <p class="mb-1">Built by: Megan Simpson</p>
          <p class="mb-0">Software Development Student</p>
        </section>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
  </div>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-d93c3Mvqd6i8x7hYaI7v55dB6Y4TRFaLMfv6VxsgQ1z0B9VIjK1Qgx9JCYFDVg71" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
